Description: 1 pair Oakley “GASCAN”Sunglasses.They are used but very well taken care of.on a scale of 1-10 I’d give them a Solid 7.5-8.The only reason I won’t go 8-8.5/9 out of 10 is due to the slight wear on the inside left arm white numbering(As you can see in the pictures)03-481/60 15 128 are the Model Number/Lens info etc.(The 1s all have a small part worn off).I think they’re polarized but I listed them non polarized as I’m not positive.The Frames & Lenses are Perfect with no Cracks,Scratches etc. Glasses come with a soft shell zip up case with Cleaning cloth and the Drawstring Carrying Bag/Cleaning cloth.Im also including a Oakley Carbon Fiber Hinged Case(Retails about 25.00)As an extra Case.The Carbon Fiber is Awesome to store the Glasses @ home,trip or for extended storage.You could throw it at a wall and it wouldn’t hurt it.So I think it’s a Pretty good deal,Glasses were about 150.00 New,Plus the Carbon Fiber Case @25.00.I think the Zip up Case is abt 10 bucks. Added Note: The white dots as seen in the pictures are reflections from the sun and the couch I took the pictures on.I assure you there are no white dots.I can send new pics if anyone emails me.I just noticed them.
